Package: leafMeAlone
Type: Package
Title: Leaf Me Alone: Monitor Urban Tree Canopy Changes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Madhura Saha
Maintainer: Madhura Saha <madhura.saha02@gmail.com>
Description: A package to detect, map, and report changes in tree canopy cover 
    using remote sensing imagery. Provides tools for NDVI-based canopy classification,
    change detection over time, autumn phenology extraction, and visualization through
    interactive maps and animated graphics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
